  "text": "While the kinematic constraints of the Magellan can be written as the unicycle model in (1), the velocities cannot be instantaneously realized. The Magellan-pro robot has an on-board control which accepts velocity commands and limits accelerations. Thus, similar to [CITATION_1] , which modeled a UAV with a similar on-board control, we utilize a first order model on the velocity inputs written as follows:",
